7)the purpose of system role when using an LLm APIs like gemini or ollama is that when using the system prompt , we can assign them a role when it can behave like that and give the answeers accurately based on the questions we opted for 

9)now you are an helpful assitant for me , answer the questions in concise and point to point structure. dont give me your predictions , i want an exact perfect answer.

